Gunmen suspected to be members of the Indigenous People of Biafra(IPOB) have reportedly killed six policemen in Ini local government area of Akwa Ibom state. The hoodlums also razed the Divisional Police Station at Odoro Ikpe, headquarters of the council area. The incident, our correspondent gathered, occurred in the early hours of Saturday. Ini is a sister local government to Ikono, which was also attacked last week during which three policemen were killed. Details shortlyâ€¦